@host = http://localhost:5278

### Login (JSON body)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "admin",
  "password": "1234"
}

###

### Lista minimal (sin JWT)
GET {{host}}/minimal/contactos

###

### Contacto por id (agregar header Authorization: Bearer <token> del login)
GET {{host}}/api/contacto/1

